From: PHLAIR <phlair@pharmaguardng.com>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 06:56:22 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Upgrade header ticker to blend live store stats with rotating
 content

- Pulls real numbers from store: stock value, product count, today's sales, low-stock count, expiring-soon count, controlled-drug count
- Interleaves live stats with shuffled regulatory reminders, health facts, and motivational lines so order/content differs every load
- Adds live-feed visual treatment: pulsing 'Live' badge, edge fade masks, dot separators
- Pauses on hover for readability
---
 src/components/layout/HeaderTicker.tsx | 151 ++++++++++++++++++++-----
 1 file changed, 121 insertions(+), 30 deletions(-)

