+];
+
+const MOTIVATION = [
+  "Every dose dispensed correctly is a life trusted to you.",
   "Stock checked today is a stockout avoided tomorrow.",
-  "A well-kept Poisons Register isn't paperwork — it's protection for your license.",
-  "The pharmacies that scale are the ones that track. Stay ahead, stay accurate.",
-  "Expiry dates don't wait for convenient timing — check inventory before it checks you.",
-  "Great pharmacists fill prescriptions. Great pharmacy owners build systems.",
-  "Compliance today saves a crisis tomorrow.",
-  "Your customers trust you with their health — give your business the same discipline.",
+  "The pharmacies that scale are the ones that track.",
   "Small daily stock checks prevent big monthly losses.",
